text: Meliboea or Meliboia (ancient Greek: Μελίβοια) was the name of a number of Greek mythological figures. Meliboea or Meliboia may also refer to: *137 Meliboea, an asteroid *Meliboea (Histiaeotis), a town in Histiaeotis district, ancient Thessaly, Greece *Meliboea (Magnesia), a town in Magnesia district, ancient Thessaly, Greece
title: Meliboea (disambiguation)
